things can be standardized, et cetera. Yeah. So I think, yeah, I totally agree with you. I think

00:30:58.979 --> 00:31:04.979
there is a fine balance over there, kind of like trying to like align with people or make people

00:31:04.979 --> 00:31:10.339
realize that by automating certain tasks that allow you to have more time to work on the things

00:31:10.339 --> 00:31:16.260
that you enjoy about. And also to ensure people that in the portfolio, there are sufficient

00:31:17.060 --> 00:31:22.500
amount of work that you will be more interesting and more impactful than kind of doing this

00:31:22.500 --> 00:31:26.420
repetitive job every day. So I think that's the approach I would take. Yeah.

00:31:27.780 --> 00:31:34.579
Totally agree. I think, you know, from a personal level, make sure it's, you know, more enjoyable.

00:31:34.579 --> 00:31:42.339
And then definitely on both Ling and my case, we just have way more work we can handle. So,

00:31:42.339 --> 00:31:49.699
and I think from business level, right, there are two ways. One is kind of not offensive,

00:31:49.699 --> 00:31:57.699
