if you just coming out of the fear, oh, I couldn't lay out people, so let's not automate,

00:32:38.819 --> 00:32:44.900
you become obsolete. You become much less efficient compared to your competitors in the same space,

00:32:44.900 --> 00:32:51.380
right? Then the company will suffer. That will be probably more a realistic risk when the company

00:32:51.380 --> 00:32:57.699
