00:50:44.020 --> 00:50:49.620
that I did, et cetera. And after reading that part, it really emphasized that treating every

00:50:49.620 --> 00:50:55.939
one-on-one meeting as an opportunity to ask your manager to help you with certain things,

00:50:56.580 --> 00:51:02.419
kind of like manage app, to ask them to take certain actions to help you or ask them to share

00:51:02.419 --> 00:51:09.139
a certain context that can help with your work. Yeah, I found that really insightful. Yeah, yeah,

